diepxuan (5.7.2+ppa~1) noble; urgency=medium

  * feat(cli): extend ductncli registry to support freebuff, claude, gemini,
    aider, llm, aichat, cursor, windsurf, continue, goose, qwen, chatgpt,
    sgpt, mod (in addition to hermes, codex, openclaw)
  * feat(cli): load user registry override from
    $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/ductn/config.yml or ~/.config/ductn/config.yml
  * feat(cli): auto-seed a default config.yml (codex, openclaw, hermes,
    freebuff) on first run when the file is absent; pre-existing
    user files are never overwritten
  * feat(cli): support DuctnCLI_AGENT_ARGS_<NAME> environment override
  * feat(cli): YAML loader gains flow-style support ([a, b], {a: 1}) so the
    default config it writes can be re-parsed by itself
  * docs(UPDATE-2026-07-20-ductncli-extend): document registry schema and
    override precedence (defaults < config < env)
  * refactor(cli): replace hard-coded agent list with AGENTS_DEFAULT +
    _resolve_agents(); hide uninstalled agents from menu and reject them
    as positional arguments (even when listed in config without binary)
  * test(cli): cover YAML loader (block + flow), registry merge, env
    override, discovery filtering, auto-seed behaviour, hermes filtering
    (27 tests, all passing)

